                                                                <MudIconButton @onclick="(() => OpenCamera(lup.LupId, lup.Oportunity, lup.Pillar))" Color="Color.Info" Size="Size.Small" Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.AddAPhoto" Disabled="@(Status == 6)"></MudIconButton>
                                                            </MudTooltip>

                                                        }

                                                        <MudChip Color="Color.Info" OnClose="Closed" Size="Size.Small" CloseIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.ChecklistRtl" Variant="Variant.Text" Style="cursor:pointer">
                                                            @if (lup.Oportunity.Length < 70)
                                                            {
                                                                @lup.Oportunity
                                                            }
                                                            else
                                                            {
                                                                @lup.Oportunity.Substring(0, 70) <span>...</span>
                                                            }
                                                        </MudChip>
                                                        @switch (lup.Status)
                                                        {
                                                            case 1:
                                                                <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Warning" Size="Size.Small">@Localizer["new"]</MudChip>
                                                                break;
                                                            case 2:
                                                                <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info" Size="Size.Small">@Localizer["inProgress"]</MudChip>
                                                                break;
                                                            case 3:
                                                                <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Small">@Localizer["finished"]</MudChip>
                                                                break;
                                                            case 4:
                                                                <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Error" Size="Size.Small">@Localizer["canceled"]</MudChip>
                                                                break;
                                                        }
                                                        <MudTooltip Text=@Localizer["deleteLupItem"] Color="Color.Error" Placement="Placement.Right" Arrow="true">
                                                            <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete" Color="Color.Error" Size="Size.Small" @onclick="(() => OpenDeleteDialog.InvokeAsync(lup.LupId))" ></MudIconButton>
                                                        </MudTooltip>
                                                    </MudButton>
                                                </MudTooltip>

                                            }
                                        }
                                        @if (capturedImages.Count > 0 && photosPillar == 5)
                                        {
                                            <MudExpansionPanels Elevation="1" MultiExpansion="true" Dense>
                                                <MudExpansionPanel IsInitiallyExpanded=true Style="min-width: 100%;" Dense>
                                                    <TitleContent>
                                                        <MudText Style="text-align: center; padding:0 !important">
                                                            @Localizer["Add Evidence Photos "]
                                                            <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Info" Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.ChecklistRtl">
                                                                ID @lupPhotosId
                                                                @if (oportunity.Length < 50)
                                                                {
                                                                    <span>&nbsp;@oportunity</span>
                                                                }
                                                                else
                                                                {
                                                                    <span>&nbsp;@oportunity.Substring(0, 50) ...</span>
                                                                }
                                                            </MudChip>
                                                        </MudText>
                                                    </TitleContent>
                                                    <ChildContent>
                                                        <MudItem Class="d-flex" Style="flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-start;">

                                                            @foreach (var (image, index) in capturedImages.Select((image, index) => (image, index)))
                                                            {
                                                                <MudItem Class=" mr-8 mb-4">
                                                                    <MudItem Style="text-align:end !important; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: -7px; cursor:pointer">
                                                                        <MudTooltip Text="Delete photo" Color="Color.Error" Placement="Placement.Right" Arrow="true">
                                                                            <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete" Color="Color.Error" @onclick="() => RemoveImage.InvokeAsync(index)"></MudIcon>
                                                                        </MudTooltip>
                                                                    </MudItem>
                                                                    <MudImage ObjectFit="ObjectFit.Cover" Height="160" Width="320" Src=@image Alt="Evidence" Elevation="25" Class="rounded-lg" />
                                                                </MudItem>
                                                            }
                                                        </MudItem>
                                                        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
                                                            <MudItem Class="mb-4">
                                                                <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled" @onclick="(() => OpenCamera(lupPhotosId, oportunity, photosPillar))" StartIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.AddAPhoto" Color="Color.Info" Disabled="@(Status == 6)">Add photo</MudButton>
                                                                @{
                                                                    string uploadMessage = "Upload Photo";
                                                                    if (capturedImages.Count > 1)
                                                                    {
                                                                        uploadMessage = "Upload " + capturedImages.Count.ToString() + " Photos";
                                                                    }
                                                                }

                                                                <MudButton Class="ml-4" Variant="Variant.Filled" @onclick="()=>UploadEvidence.InvokeAsync(lupPhotosId)" StartIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.FileUpload" Color="Color.Primary" Disabled="@(Status == 6)">@uploadMessage</MudButton>
                                                            </MudItem>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </ChildContent>
                                                </MudExpansionPanel>
                                            </MudExpansionPanels>
                                        }
                                    }
                                    @if (_tempLup.Count > 0)
                                    {
                                        foreach (var lup in _tempLup.Keys)
                                        {
                                            if (lup.Pillar == 5)
                                            {
                                                <MudTooltip Text=@Localizer["lupWillBeCreatedWhenTheCreateJobObservationButtonIsClicked"] Color="Color.Info" Placement="Placement.Bottom" Arrow="true">
                                                    <MudButton Style="padding: 0px; margin-right: 10px; margin-top: 10px" Color="Color.Info" Variant="Variant.Outlined" Disabled="@(Status == 6)">
                                                        <MudTooltip Text="Take photo" Color="Color.Info" Placement="Placement.Right" Arrow="true">
                                                            <MudIconButton @onclick="(() => OpenTempCamera(lup))"
                                                                           Color="Color.Info"
                                                                           Size="Size.Small"
                                                                           Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.AddAPhoto" Disabled="@(Status == 6)">
                                                            </MudIconButton>
                                                        </MudTooltip>
                                                        <MudChip Color="Color.Info" OnClose="Closed" Size="Size.Small" CloseIcon="@Icons.Material.Filled.ChecklistRtl" Variant="Variant.Text" Style="cursor:pointer">
                                                            @if (lup.Oportunity.Length < 70)
                                                            {
                                                                @lup.Oportunity
                                                            }
                                                            else
                                                            {
                                                                @lup.Oportunity.Substring(0, 70) <span>...</span>
                                                            }
                                                        </MudChip>
                                                        <MudText>
                                                            <MudChip Variant="Variant.Text" Color="Color.Success" Size="Size.Small" Style="cursor:pointer">New</MudChip>
                                                        </MudText>
                                                        @if (_tempLup[lup].Count > 0)
                                                        {
                                                            <MudItem Class="d-flex" Style="flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-start;">

                                                                @foreach (var (image, index) in _tempLup[lup].Select((image, index) => (image, index)))
                                                                {
                                                                    <MudItem Class="mr-8">
                                                                        <MudItem Style="text-align:end !important; margin-right: -16px; margin-bottom: -20px; cursor:pointer">
                                                                            <MudTooltip Text="Delete photo" Color="Color.Error" Placement="Placement.Right" Arrow="true">
                                                                                <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Delete" Size="Size.Small" Color="Color.Error" @onclick="() => RemoveTempImage.InvokeAsync((lup, index))"></MudIcon>
                                                                            </MudTooltip>
                                                                        </MudItem>
                                                                        <MudImage ObjectFit="ObjectFit.Cover" Height="40" Width="80" Src=@image Alt="Evidence" Elevation="25" Class="rounded-lg" />
                                                                    </MudItem>
                                                                }
                                                            </MudItem>
                                                        }
                                                        <MudTooltip Text=@Localizer["deleteLupItem"] Color="Color.Error" Placement="Placement.Right" Arrow="true">
                                                            <MudIconButton Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Cancel" Color="Color.Error" Size="Size.Small" @onclick="(() => DeleteTempLup.InvokeAsync(lup))" Disabled="@(Status == 6)"></MudIconButton>
                                                        </MudTooltip>
                                                    </MudButton>
                                                </MudTooltip>

                                            }
                                        }

                                    }
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </MudSimpleTable>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </MudSimpleTable>
</MudExpansionPanel>

@code {
    [Parameter]
    public string title { get; set; } = "";
    [Parameter]
    public Dictionary<string, Glosary> _glosaryInfo { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public int auxErgonomicsLevel { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public int? Status { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public List<LupOpportunity> area_ListS { get; set; } = new List<LupOpportunity>();
    [Parameter]
    public List<LupOpportunity> area_ListQ { get; set; } = new List<LupOpportunity>();
    [Parameter]
    public List<LupOpportunity> area_ListD { get; set; } = new List<LupOpportunity>();
    [Parameter]
    public List<LupOpportunity> area_ListC { get; set; } = new List<LupOpportunity>();
    [Parameter]
    public List<LupOpportunity> area_ListOther { get; set; } = new List<LupOpportunity>();
    [Parameter]
    public JobObservation _lupJobObservations { get; set; } = new();
    [Parameter]
    public List<string> capturedImages { get; set; } = new List<string>();
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<Lup> SetLup { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public Dictionary<Lup, List<string>> _tempLup { get; set; } = new();

    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<(int, int)> RemoveFromList { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<int> AddTempLup { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback OpenCameraDialog { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback OpenTempCameraDialog { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<int> OpenDeleteDialog { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<int> RemoveImage { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<int> UploadEvidence { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<Lup> DeleteTempLup { get; set; }
    [Parameter]
    public EventCallback<(Lup, int)> RemoveTempImage { get; set; }

    private async void OpenGuideDialog(int pillarID)
    {
        var parameters = new DialogParameters
            {
                { "selectedPillar", pillarID }
            };
        var dialog = await DialogService.ShowAsync<Guide_Dialog>("", parameters, dialogGuideOptions);
        await dialog.Result;

    }
    private DialogOptions dialogGuideOptions = new() { CloseOnEscapeKey = true, MaxWidth = MaxWidth.Medium, FullWidth = true, Position = DialogPosition.TopCenter };

    void Closed(MudChip chip)
    {
        // react to chip closed
    }


    private DialogOptions dialogLup = new() { CloseOnEscapeKey = true, MaxWidth = MaxWidth.Large, FullWidth = true };

    private async void OpenDialogLup(int id)
    {
        var parameters = new DialogParameters { { "lupId", id } };
        var dialog = DialogService.Show<OpenLup_Dialog>("", parameters, dialogLup);
        await dialog.Result;
    }

    public int lupPhotosId = 0;
    public string oportunity = "";
    public int photosPillar = 0;

    private void OpenCamera(int lupId, string lupOportunity, int pillar)
    {
        photosPillar = pillar;
        oportunity = lupOportunity;
        lupPhotosId = lupId;

        OpenCameraDialog.InvokeAsync();
    }

    private void OpenTempCamera(Lup lup)
    {
        photosPillar = lup.Pillar;
        oportunity = lup.Oportunity;

        SetLup.InvokeAsync(lup);
        OpenTempCameraDialog.InvokeAsync();
    }
}
